definitions.definition: A small settlement near Loch Creran , north-east of Oban , Argyll and Bute council area, Scotland ( OS grid ref NM9641 ) .
A local government area in central-west Queensland , Australia ; in full, Barcaldine Region .
A rural town within Barcaldine Region, Queensland .
